    start([Start]) --> getName[Get name argument]
    getName --> getInfo[WorkspaceService getWorkspaceInfo]
    getInfo --> checkExists{Workspace dir exists?}
    checkExists -->|no| errorNotFound[Output error - not found]
    checkExists -->|yes| output{JSON output?}
    output -->|yes| jsonSuccess[Output JSON with info]
    output -->|no| printInfo[Print workspace details]
    printInfo --> checkProjects{Has projects?}
